Denzel Washington in Flight (2012)

In real life, Washington rarely drinks, and during an interview promoting his movie Flight, he claimed he would never play a role genuinely drunk, as the results he has seen, have been invariably embarrassing. Washington further added that he made a point to never drink during filming so as to not become fascinated with alcohol while playing an alcoholic. He did however gain weight to have a realistic bloated belly of a heavy drinker🍺
